title: List Bond as Collateral Asset
body:
Summary
List BOND as collateral asset, staring with 0% collateral factor.

**For**: List bond as collateral asset
**Against**: Do nothing

Background
Diversity of token list has always been the advantage of C.R.E.A.M. Finance Lending. By continually listing new token like BOND, we increase this advantage of protocol and expand our influence to reach more people, allowing more and more hodlers to leverage their tokens in a diversifying way.
author: 0xb6e362900B7113F246A7e1c17E9746b3B9C079dB
